{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, the system should also provide more control to the users so that they feel more comfortable using the system.",
    "It can be concluded that Facebook users desire explanations to make informed decisions.",
    "The participants talked about being \"frightened\" by social media due to suspicious activity.",
    "Hence, they do not want to be in the dark regarding content recommendations.",
    "To be informed about social media data privacy and security Our observation shows that Facebook users are skeptical of their online security, especially regarding their data."
  ]
}